 x_{n+1}^2=\frac14\left(x_n+\frac{a}{x_n}\right)^2=\frac14\left(x_n-\frac{a}{x_n}\right)^2+a\ge a\tag{1} 
 x_{n+1}-x_n=\frac{a-x_n^2}{2x_n}\le0\tag{2} 
